[SHORT DESC]
Heals 50% max HP.

[LONG DESC]
<p>Recovers 50% of the user's max HP.
</p>
<h2>Related Moves</h2>
<p><a href="/dp/moves/milk_drink">Milk Drink</a> is identical.<br/ >
<a href="/dp/moves/recover">Recover</a> is identical.<br/ >
<a href="/dp/moves/softboiled">Softboiled</a> is identical.<br/ >
<a href="/dp/moves/moonlight">Moonlight</a> is an equivalent move, but is affected by the weather.<br/ >
<a href="/dp/moves/morning_sun">Morning Sun</a> is an equivalent move, but is affected by the weather.<br/ >
<a href="/dp/moves/synthesis">Synthesis</a> is a Grass-type equivalent, but is affected by the weather.<br/ >
<a href="/dp/moves/wish">Wish</a> is an equivalent move, but HP is recovered at the end of the second turn.</p>